WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.900 --> 00:00:05.900
 Green Ninja! Green Ninja! Keep the children clean! 

00:00:05.900 --> 00:00:08.800
 Green Ninja! Green Ninja! Build a ninja team! 

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:11.500
 Green Ninja! Green Ninja! Drag racing, recycling! 

00:00:11.500 --> 00:00:15.800
 Green Ninja! Green Ninja! Never stop before we do! 

00:00:15.800 --> 00:00:18.179
 Green Ninja! 

00:00:18.179 --> 00:00:23.000
 In this episode of "Green Ninja Show", Barnaby from Kona, Hawaii asked: 

00:00:28.830 --> 00:00:31.500
 Dude, what is the foam? 

00:00:31.500 --> 00:00:34.000
 Bubble people? ! 

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:38.720
 Let me tell you the story about the bubble man! 

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:45.720
 Although I was little known at the beginning, I knew that I was destined to accomplish something big. 

00:00:51.500 --> 00:00:56.000
 The bubble people will take over the world. 

00:01:49.300 --> 00:01:56.789
 My influence started small... But day by day, my existence grows again... 

00:02:00.670 --> 00:02:08.000
 Even if they still keep me, I have not really disappeared. 

00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:26.000
 Soon, I am everywhere. I completely take possession of them. 

00:02:58.580 --> 00:03:01.500
 Even the green ninja can't stop me. 

00:03:01.500 --> 00:03:06.000
 He tried to use degradable containers and paper bags... 

00:03:06.000 --> 00:03:07.810
 But he can't deal with me alone, 

00:03:07.810 --> 00:03:12.000
 I am unstoppable. 

00:03:36.070 --> 00:03:43.070
 I have ruled the world. Nowhere I could not arrive. 

00:04:21.000 --> 00:04:23.520
 But then... he appeared again! 

00:04:23.520 --> 00:04:30.000
 And this time... he is not alone! 

00:04:40.000 --> 00:04:47.000
 These bans against me have led people to oppose me one by one in the city. I started to lose my leadership. 

00:05:02.500 --> 00:05:09.000
 Now... they even want to keep me out of the country! 

00:05:31.000 --> 00:05:33.000
 Dude, we heard it. 

00:05:33.000 --> 00:05:36.000
 Buddy, we are here to support you. 

00:05:36.000 --> 00:05:40.000
 Dude, we have had the same situation. 

00:05:51.000 --> 00:06:10.000
